{"tid":303279,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平第二日出巡　運輸署上午全港交通直播死機","createTime":"2017-06-30T05:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T05:40:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8190f8cb087783c7b59e506b987428641cdbcab7","tid":303279,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170630/large/1498794364_5b1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170630%2Flarge%2F1498794364_5b1a.jpg&h=96d38ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平訪港，港府海陸空嚴密佈防。有區議員就發現今早起運輸署即時交通監測系統的CCTV畫面突然全數「熄機」，嚴重影響駕駛者，不排除是為遷就習近平的保安安排。運輸署初步回覆就指已發現系統無畫面，但稱是系統故障所致。直至中午12點45分，直播畫面才恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者上午11點登上運輸署網站查看，發現無論是各主要道路實時交通快拍，或是港九、荃灣及屯門公路視像直播的各個CCTV，均顯示「暫時未能提供服務」的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n南區區議員柴文瀚表示，不少駕駛者習慣每天出門前觀看運輸署提供的實時交通畫面，以避開塞車的路段，但今早上班繁忙時間前已發現全港系統均無畫面顯示，「但顯示過海時間幾多分鐘、邊條隧道嗰啲資料就正常顯示」。<br />\n<br />\n他指以往監測系統偶然會出現系統問題，但未試過如此長時間、大規模故障，「可能佢（運輸署）以為保安理由需要閂啦！」他批評運輸署至少應該通知使用者系統受影響，「如果佢有視像嘅問題，佢應該老實同人講囉！唔理佢係因為習近平喺度好、updated緊好、冧咗都好，出一句訊息話受影響唔會錯㗎嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n運輸署稱今早已發現系統無畫面顯示，但否認是與習近平訪港有關，只稱目前正在搶修系統。"},{"pid":"2fbb022713ae104f29d69e79ce040a4d8a897da5","tid":303279,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170630&amp;guid=56895280&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170630%26guid%3D56895280%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=KtAiQ8SDkA72PzGucwi2MR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=3b379095\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170630%26guid%3D56895280%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=5f9ab782\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170630&amp;guid=56895280&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"4c0e8f69f9b0dab94bff32867c23ee84b9f4c3c7","tid":303279,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"移動性地區戒嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd5b78ea4e547a9aa3869cde48431a7918dc25e","tid":303279,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340fe45c3c78f3d18aabff1ba4565831ce04d5d8","tid":303279,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"皇帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211e7349e26db5ee275bbad78672e3a5088e784f","tid":303279,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54438dd0e9eeacd64522900d99597e18a24f152b","tid":303279,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b491d1bbee5f59185c0dbc4109d026a7bb1437b5","tid":303279,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}